To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private SchaffTrendCycle _stc;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_stc = STC(symbol, cyclePeriod, fastPeriod, slowPeriod);

// In OnData()
if (_stc.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "schafftrendcycle", _stc.Current.Value);
}
